{
  "title": "Rich Fluffy Egyptian Soy Milk Casserole",
  "description": "A sour and fluffy Egyptian dish featuring soy milk, perfect for midnight cravings, with an en-croute crust and ayurvedic-tamasic friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
